Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.29,0:00:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,不能动哟 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.29,0:00:09.80,Default,,0,0,0,,对~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.96,0:00:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,得手啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:12.30,Default,,0,0,0,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.51,0:00:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.88,0:00:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊呀呀呀呀！失败啦 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.76,0:00:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咕咚~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.97,0:00:18.72,Default,,0,0,0,,咕咚
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.18,0:00:20.60,Default,,0,0,0,,铛
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.97,0:00:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么啦？赛莲！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.77,0:00:27.77,Default,,0,0,0,,难不成你放弃收集音符了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.90,0:00:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么可能！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.77,0:00:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我想到一口气使全世界
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.78,0:00:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,陷入不幸的究极作战
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.49,0:00:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,究极作战？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.94,0:00:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,首先
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.95,0:00:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把一直在哈米身边的音符精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.87,0:00:42.66,Default,,0,0,0,,音调精灵给夺过来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.79,0:00:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,音调精灵？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.83,0:00:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.96,0:00:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米它们收集的音符
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.83,0:00:50.71,Default,,0,0,0,,全都由音调精灵持有着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.96,0:00:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,将其夺过来与我们收集的音符相互结合起来
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.97,0:00:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不幸的乐谱就能一口气接近完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,然后
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.93,0:01:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,我的歌声把音符印刻在传说中的乐谱上面
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.94,0:01:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在一段时间内
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.94,0:01:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,会让人们悲伤下去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.94,0:01:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,在这一段时间里...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.94,0:01:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,把剩下的音符都收集起来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.94,0:01:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,将不幸的乐谱完成
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.90,0:01:17.41,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这么一回事！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.66,0:01:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是梅菲斯特大人
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.95,0:01:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,音调精灵在我们这一边的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.87,0:01:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女也无法出手吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,的确是究极的作战
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.83,0:01:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,但是音调精灵有这么简单夺到吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.96,0:01:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,利用与过去曾经是好朋友哈米关系的话
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.97,0:01:36.72,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你至今为止好多次
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.97,0:01:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,都被和哈米的友情给动摇了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.55,0:01:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请你相信我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.76,0:01:43.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经不会再犹豫了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.93,0:01:46.73,Default,,0,0,0,,为此我希望
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.94,0:01:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,能再一次对我的心灵打入邪恶噪音
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.02,0:01:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.15,0:01:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,好吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我就把至今为止最为强力的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.94,0:01:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,究极的噪音打入给你吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.95,0:02:00.62,Default,,0,0,0,,友情 爱情 相信的心
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.87,0:02:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,那种东西全是虚幻的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.76,0:02:20.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 哈哈 哈哈 哈哈 ~哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.84,0:02:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哇哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.93,0:02:24.72,Default,,0,0,0,,把所有幸福消灭
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.93,0:02:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,使世界被不幸的旋律给笼罩
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.93,0:02:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是你的使命
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:32.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.94,0:02:34.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你就不会再被友情什么的给打动了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.94,0:02:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲哟
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.94,0:02:38.74,Default,,0,0,0,,成为邪恶的化身吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.74,0:02:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,光之美少女 哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.95,0:02:44.70,Default,,0,0,0,,让你们看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.95,0:02:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你们居住的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.95,0:02:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,将被悲伤的颜色所浸染的样子
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.96,0:02:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.96,0:02:53.71,Default,,0,0,0,,睡得真好 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.84,0:02:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,咿哑
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:55.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,音符们去哪了 喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.96,0:02:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈喵 抓住音符了啊 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.72,0:03:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:32.70,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.95,0:04:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊啊啊啊！赛莲 最后的作战 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.92,0:04:43.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗啦~喵噗啦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.96,0:04:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿哟 嘿哟
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.96,0:04:47.71,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚的音符也抓住了！喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.88,0:04:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodo 哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.97,0:04:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米是普通的猫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.97,0:04:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看那个 Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.22,0:04:54.51,Default,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:55.72,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.93,0:04:59.73,Default,,0,0,0,,是赛莲 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.93,0:05:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.85,0:05:01.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你怎么了？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.94,0:05:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,和你没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.94,0:05:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么会没关系 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.94,0:05:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米和赛莲是朋友 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.74,0:05:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呃呃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.86,0:05:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,梅菲斯特大人对我讲
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.87,0:05:17.74,Default,,0,0,0,,[我已经不需要你了]
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.95,0:05:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,吔！！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.95,0:05:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么 喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.96,0:05:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,因为不管多久
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.96,0:05:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,也收集不完音符啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.96,0:05:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我头脑一热
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.96,0:05:29.71,Default,,0,0,0,,和他吵架逃出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.97,0:05:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大事不妙啊！喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.97,0:05:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.97,0:05:35.51,Default,,0,0,0,,你想做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:37.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我背你 一起逃吧！喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.31,0:05:41.89,Default,,0,0,0,,哈啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.89,0:05:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲可是哈米我最好的朋友 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.94,0:05:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.74,0:05:51.74,Default,,0,0,0,,呃呃
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.90,0:05:52.78,Default,,0,0,0,,不好意思
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:53.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Rere
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,大家！先回去吧 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.95,0:05:58.74,Default,,0,0,0,,吭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:06.75,Default,,0,0,0,,这里的话 谁都找不到 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.96,0:06:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,暂时先休息一下吧！喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.96,0:06:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.96,0:06:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,听到赛莲的感谢真是久违了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.76,0:06:16.76,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 独自饿了吗？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我把好吃的东西拿过来 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.97,0:06:19.76,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下哟 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.98,0:06:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下哟 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.85,0:06:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哼！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.94,0:06:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,把珍藏的点心给她 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,喵~ 哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.78,0:06:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲会很高兴的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.95,0:06:39.58,Default,,0,0,0,,吭
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.95,0:06:40.12,Default,,0,0,0,,撲
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.95,0:06:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.56,0:06:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,响 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.56,0:06:46.56,Default,,0,0,0,,要去哪里咩？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.96,0:06:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！这个行李难道是要离家出走咩！？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.96,0:06:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,不...不 不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.96,0:06:53.67,Default,,0,0,0,,稍...稍微散步一下 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.97,0:06:54.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那再见 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.76,0:06:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.51,0:06:59.97,Default,,0,0,0,,噢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.97,0:07:01.47,Default,,0,0,0,,到底在做什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.77,0:07:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.48,0:07:05.48,Default,,0,0,0,,响 对不起 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.77,0:07:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,但是赛莲的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.98,0:07:08.77,Default,,0,0,0,,对任何人都得保密 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.90,0:07:10.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.94,0:07:13.78,Default,,0,0,0,,喵呜
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.94,0:07:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,普通的猫吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.74,0:07:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲 哈米我绝对要好好保护你 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.74,0:07:23.75,Default,,0,0,0,,呷 呷 呷 呷
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.75,0:07:26.75,Default,,0,0,0,,多吃点 打起精神来 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.96,0:07:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 还记得吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.96,0:07:34.76,Default,,0,0,0,,以前在森林里经常一起练习歌唱呢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.97,0:07:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.97,0:07:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真怀念啊 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:40.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.97,0:07:44.56,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！被什么人发现的话该怎么办啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.77,0:07:45.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈 对不起 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.64,0:07:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,ReRe
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.98,0:07:50.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 哈米 我想过了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.77,0:07:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:55.57,Default,,0,0,0,,我不做坏事了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.78,0:07:58.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米 做你们的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.74,0:08:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,嘻~呵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.74,0:08:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,说...说点什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.74,0:08:04.95,Default,,0,0,0,,这不是很难为情吗？我可是鼓起勇气说的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.75,0:08:08.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真高兴 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.75,0:08:10.54,Default,,0,0,0,,终于和赛莲在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:12.54,Default,,0,0,0,,没有比这更高兴的事情了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.75,0:08:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,终于能实现梦想了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.75,0:08:16.55,Default,,0,0,0,,梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.97,0:08:18.76,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.84,0:08:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,是和我一起演唱幸福的旋律吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.05,0:08:23.55,Default,,0,0,0,,没错 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.75,0:08:24.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.97,0:08:26.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我真的想和哈米一起演唱哟
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.98,0:08:28.77,Default,,0,0,0,,真的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.98,0:08:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那马上开始快乐地练习 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.98,0:08:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.94,0:08:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,喂！又发出这么大的声音
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.94,0:08:36.78,Default,,0,0,0,,这次练习歌唱 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.94,0:08:38.78,Default,,0,0,0,,换赛莲来唱 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.95,0:08:39.78,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.95,0:08:43.74,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~啊~啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.95,0:08:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~啊~啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.95,0:08:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodo！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.96,0:08:51.75,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~啊~啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.75,0:08:53.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.00,0:08:54.75,Default,,0,0,0,,歌声？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.71,0:08:56.55,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.96,0:08:58.76,Default,,0,0,0,,是哈米啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.97,0:08:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,旁边的猫？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,谁知道呢 是哈米的朋友吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.97,0:09:06.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 走吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.97,0:09:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.98,0:09:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哈 今日真的好开心喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.94,0:09:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哈
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.94,0:09:17.78,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 我有个请求
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.94,0:09:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.95,0:09:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,用这些音符来实现梦想吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.95,0:09:27.74,Default,,0,0,0,,实现梦想？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.87,0:09:31.87,Default,,0,0,0,,把收集到的音符互相结合
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.96,0:09:34.75,Default,,0,0,0,,在一起演唱幸福的旋律吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.21,0:09:36.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哇！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.96,0:09:38.76,Default,,0,0,0,,呜喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.67,0:09:39.96,Default,,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.96,0:09:41.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.76,Default,,0,0,0,,即使哈米与赛莲的音符
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.97,0:09:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,加在一起也肯定凑不齐的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.97,0:09:47.76,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.93,0:09:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,只要我们一起演唱幸福的旋律
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.93,0:09:52.81,Default,,0,0,0,,梅菲斯特他们肯定会慌张的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.94,0:09:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,趁此机会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.90,0:09:55.94,Default,,0,0,0,,找出剩下的音符就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.06,0:09:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,原来如此！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.94,0:09:58.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是赛莲 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.94,0:10:00.53,Default,,0,0,0,,那马上和响她们商量看看 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.74,0:10:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,不行哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.90,0:10:03.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好好想想 哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.86,0:10:07.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那两个人是看不到音符的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.03,0:10:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,首先得由我们两个加油
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.95,0:10:11.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但是！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.96,0:10:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们遇到危机的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.96,0:10:15.75,Default,,0,0,0,,让她们变成光之美少女来救我们吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.96,0:10:16.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.96,0:10:17.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.96,0:10:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.96,0:10:22.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那明天请把音调精灵给带过来吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.97,0:10:23.76,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.88,0:10:25.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.97,0:10:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,啊~啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.98,0:10:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:35.77,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米真好啊 没有作业
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.98,0:10:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,今日好像心情很好啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.94,0:10:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么好事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.94,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！是秘密 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:41.78,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！是秘密 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.94,0:10:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那是什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.94,0:10:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,真让人在意呀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.95,0:10:48.74,Default,,0,0,0,,明天一起去赛莲那儿 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.94,0:10:50.64,Default,,0,0,0,,真期待 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.95,0:10:52.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:10:55.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喵哈~哈~哈~哈
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.92,0:10:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.96,0:10:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！哈米的样子很奇怪？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.96,0:11:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 黑色的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.84,0:11:03.76,Default,,0,0,0,,额头上有红色的花纹呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.43,0:11:05.80,Default,,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.04,0:11:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 是赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.97,0:11:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,那只猫有着可怕的眼神
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.97,0:11:12.77,Default,,0,0,0,,昨天那个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.97,0:11:13.77,Default,,0,0,0,,告诉她们吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.89,0:11:14.56,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯~
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.73,0:11:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.37,0:11:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,但愿没有被卷入奇怪的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.96,0:11:39.13,Default,,0,0,0,,喵~喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.25,0:11:39.29,Default,,0,0,0,,喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.96,0:11:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.71,0:11:42.71,Default,,0,0,0,,响 奏
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.96,0:11:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你们会在这种地方 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.09,0:11:49.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米才是
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.89,0:11:51.72,Default,,0,0,0,,那么 赛莲在哪儿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.89,0:11:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你在讲什么啊！喵
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.93,0:11:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米 不可以说谎哟
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.93,0:11:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米的谎话马上就能看穿的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.94,0:12:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.94,0:12:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,其...其实 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.74,0:12:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲说想成为我们的伙伴 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.07,0:12:10.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.95,0:12:12.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这句话一定是骗人的哟
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.95,0:12:14.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们无法相信
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.91,Default,,0,0,0,,一定在计划着什么 不会错的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.54,0:12:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:21.71,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲讲了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.96,0:12:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,一直想成为伙伴
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.96,0:12:26.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你不是一再这样被欺骗吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.97,0:12:28.72,Default,,0,0,0,,是真的 真的真的...是真的喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.97,0:12:30.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米我相信赛莲 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.97,0:12:31.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.93,0:12:33.72,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.93,0:12:34.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.06,0:12:40.73,Default,,0,0,0,,响与奏都不知道真正的赛莲 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.94,0:12:42.73,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲是哈米一起演唱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:45.69,Default,,0,0,0,,幸福的旋律歌姬 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.94,0:12:50.74,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲是哈米最重要的最好朋友 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.95,0:12:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodo
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:12:59.71,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.96,0:13:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗 喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:02.71,Default,,0,0,0,,迟到了真的对不起 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.96,0:13:06.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信你会来的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.96,0:13:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.96,0:13:08.72,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯喵
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.97,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 到乐谱身边去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.72,Default,,0,0,0,,演唱幸福的旋律吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.93,0:13:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,拿着音符的音调精灵 是哪一个？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.93,0:13:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
