Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.97,0:13:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米被欺骗了 Rere
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.97,0:13:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:14:00.73,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲！等等我 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.93,0:14:02.73,Default,,0,0,0,,喵~嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.94,0:14:05.73,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.94,0:14:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不会让你逃掉了 赛莲
