Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.95,0:14:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是哈米与赛莲的音符 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.95,0:14:18.70,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.49,0:14:19.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,喵 啊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.95,0:14:24.71,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲愿意保护哈米吗？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.96,0:14:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,当然
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.96,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,无论如何都不打算交出音符啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.96,0:14:31.71,Default,,0,0,0,,那么这个如何
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.96,0:14:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,出来吧 负向音调
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.94,0:14:48.73,Default,,0,0,0,,负向音调！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.94,0:14:50.73,Default,,0,0,0,,啊！
