Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.76,0:20:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,喵噗
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.76,0:20:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,今日大成功啊 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.48,0:20:18.73,Default,,0,0,0,,成功了 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.98,0:20:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Dodo Rere
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.94,0:20:22.57,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.73,0:20:23.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你看 喵
