Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.90,0:20:26.57,Default,,0,0,0,,托赛莲的福
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.69,0:20:28.74,Default,,0,0,0,,音符有好多哟 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.95,0:20:29.63,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.83,0:20:30.93,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.95,0:20:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,喵啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.75,0:20:38.75,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.75,0:20:43.54,Default,,0,0,0,,呐 不是说要一起去乐谱那里吗 喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.54,0:20:45.54,Default,,0,0,0,,说什么呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.78,0:20:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,喵？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.96,0:20:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,去小调岛的是我一个人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.97,0:20:51.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你要留在这里哟
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.97,0:20:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？喵
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.89,0:20:55.56,Default,,0,0,0,,不明白吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.89,0:20:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你啊 又被骗了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.48,0:21:01.48,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.77,0:21:03.44,Default,,0,0,0,,哦 是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.90,0:21:05.44,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.69,0:21:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,果然
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.69,0:21:07.44,Default,,0,0,0,,别动
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.49,0:21:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,音调精灵会怎么样也没关系吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.91,0:21:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,叱~
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,呵呵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.70,0:21:16.45,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.70,0:21:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢了 给我音符
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.88,0:21:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,做得漂亮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.68,0:21:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,世界将会充满着悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.81,0:21:37.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是我们胜利了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.81,0:21:40.56,Default,,0,0,0,,哈哈哈哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.90,0:21:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,音符 全部都到了小调岛的手中
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.48,0:21:50.78,Default,,0,0,0,,呐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.90,0:21:52.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这样一来 如果赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.66,0:21:54.57,Default,,0,0,0,,演唱“不幸的旋律”的话
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.78,0:21:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,世界会结束吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.74,0:21:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米相信着 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.91,0:22:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哎！
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.91,0:22:02.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.92,0:22:05.75,Default,,0,0,0,,哈米相信着赛莲 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.72,0:23:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,绝对不会让不幸的旋律唱起的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.93,0:23:48.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会保护大家的笑容给你看
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.77,0:23:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,赛莲
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:51.77,Default,,0,0,0,,不要唱了 喵！
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.86,0:23:52.73,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？那一道光是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:53.49,0:23:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,有谁要出来了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.90,0:23:56.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那是新的光之美少女 喵
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.90,0:23:58.70,Default,,0,0,0,,新的光之美少女？
